ploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-Pin-2.jpg" data-pin-title="Aloo Tikki - Indian-Spiced Potato Patties" data-pin-description="Easy 25-minute recipe for┬ĀAloo Tikki,┬Āa popular north-Indian street food! Mashed┬Āpotato and peas are formed into patties then pan-fried until golden brown and crispy. #indianrecipes #indianvegetarianrecipes #indiansnackrecipe"  alt="plate of aloo tikki and chutney titled &quot;Crispy Indian Potato Patties. Aloo Tikki&quot;" class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner" loading="lazy" /></noscript></div><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="683" height="1024" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20683%201024'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-pin-media="https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-Pin-1.jpg" data-pin-title="Aloo Tikki - Indian-Spiced Potato Patties" data-pin-description="Easy 25-minute recipe for┬ĀAloo Tikki,┬Āa popular north-Indian street food! Mashed┬Āpotato and peas are formed into patties then pan-fried until golden brown and crispy. #indianrecipes #indianvegetarianrecipes #indiansnackrecipe"  alt="picture of aloo tikki on a plate with chutneys titled &quot;Crispy &amp; Tasty Aloo Tikki. Indian Spiced Potato Patties&quot;" class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner  dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-single" data-lazy-src="https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-Pin-1-683x1024.jpg" /><noscript><img width="683" height="1024" src="https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-Pin-1-683x1024.jpg" data-pin-media="https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-Pin-1.jpg" data-pin-title="Aloo Tikki - Indian-Spiced Potato Patties" data-pin-description="Easy 25-minute recipe for┬ĀAloo Tikki,┬Āa popular north-Indian street food! Mashed┬Āpotato and peas are formed into patties then pan-fried until golden brown and crispy. #indianrecipes #indianvegetarianrecipes #indiansnackrecipe"  alt="picture of aloo tikki on a plate with chutneys titled &quot;Crispy &amp; Tasty Aloo Tikki. Indian Spiced Potato Patties&quot;" class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner  dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-single" loading="lazy" /></noscript></div><span id="dpsp-post-content-markup" data-image-pin-it="true"></span>
<p><meta charset="utf-8">Easy 25-minute recipe for&nbsp;<strong>Aloo Tikki,&nbsp;</strong>an extremely popular north-Indian street food. Mashed potatoes, green peas, herbs, and seasonings are combined and formed into patties, then pan-fried until golden brown and crispy. </p>



<p>Enjoy them with <a href="https://spicecravings.com/cilantro-chutney-green-chutney">cilantro</a> and <a href="https://spicecravings.com/tamarind-chutney">tamarind chutney</a>, with a cup of <a href="https://spicecravings.com/masala-chai">chai</a>, or combine with spiced yogurt for&nbsp;classic <em>Aloo Tikki Chaat</em>!</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" fetchpriority="high" data-pin-description="Easy 25-minute recipe for┬ĀAloo Tikki,┬Āa popular north-Indian street food! Mashed┬Āpotato and peas are formed into patties then pan-fried until golden brown and crispy. #indianrecipes #indianvegetarianrecipes #indiansnackrecipe" data-pin-title="Aloo Tikki (Indian-Spiced Potato Patties)" src="https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-New.jpg" alt="overhead of a plate filled with indian potato patties with a side of two chutneys" data-skip-lazy class="wp-image-31518" srcset="https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-New.jpg 1200w, https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-New-200x300.jpg 200w, https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-New-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-New-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-New-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-New-720x1080.jpg 720w, https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-New-360x540.jpg 360w, https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-New-180x270.jpg 180w, https://spicecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Aloo-Tikki-New-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure><style type="text/css"></style>    <div class="dpsp-email-save-this-tool " style="background-color: #fef9f5;">        <div class="hubbub-save-this-form-wrapper"><h3 class="hubbub-save-this-heading">Want to save this recipe?</h3><div class="hubbub-save-this-message"><p>We'll email this post to you, so you can come back to it later!</p></div><div class="hubbub-save-this-form-only-wrapper"><form name="hubbub-save-this-form" method="post" action="">                    <input type="text" name="hubbub-save-this-snar