<h2 id="aloo-tikki"   class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold">Aloo Tikki</h2>
<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
<span class="wprm-recipe-details wprm-recipe-author wprm-block-text-light"><a href="https://spicecravings.com/about-spice-cravings" target="_self">Aneesha Gupta</a></span>
<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">Easy 25-minute recipe for┬ĀAloo Tikki,┬Āa popular north-Indian street food! Mashed┬Āpotato and peas are formed into patties then pan-fried until golden brown and crispy. </span></div>
<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
