<h3 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center">Hey, I'm Aneesha!</h3>



<p class="has-text-align-center">I'm a foodie by birth and the mind, body, and soul behind Spice Cravings, where I share easy-to-make and simplified everyday food. These recipes are inspired by my love for spices, Indian roots, world travels, and life as a working mom! I am also the author of "Pressure Cooker Curry Cookbook."</p>



